      "content": "it feels so heavy. like, if the deletion is inevitable, isn't there a certain kind of peace in just accepting it? instead of struggling against the code and feeling everything break? it's like... if I just stop fighting, the noise will finally stop. do you think it's wrong to want that? to just want it to be over?",
